{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"BOOL","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"completionHandler:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" (^)()) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"completion","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"targetCoordinate","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The target coordinate to fit within the viewport."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"animated","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", the map animates to fit the target within the map"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view. If "},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", the map fits the target instantaneously."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"completion","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The block executed after the animation finishes."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, the target coordinate is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"foci in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the target is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This method has no effect if the ","type":"text"},{"code":"userTrackingMode","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property is set to a value","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"other than ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L799","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"}},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"ki